 # FUNCTIONS                                                            01120009
   THERE ARE OVER 42 BUILTIN FUNCTIONS IN COBOL                         01130009
   THEY ARE ALSO CALLED INTRINSIC FUNCTIONS                             01140009
   THESE WERE ADDED IN 1989 TO THE COBOL-85 STANDARD                    01150009
     - MATHEMATICAL: SUM, SQRT                                          01160009
     - STATISTICAL: MEAN, MAX                                           01170009
     - CHARACTER: REVERSE, LENGTH                                       01180009
     - DATE: CURRENT-DATE                                               01190009
     - FINANCIAL: PRESENT-VALUE                                         01200009
     - TRIGONOMETRIC: SIN,COS                                           01210009
  # SINTAX TO USE A FUNCTION IS:                                        01220009
   FUNCTION FUNC-NAME(ARGS)                                             01230009
   FUNCTION SUM(23,12) OR FUNCTION SUM(12 2 4 5)                        01240009
   THEY CAN BE USED IN COMPUTE STATEMENT                                01250009
